event.title: The deaths could be a result of a drier than normal winter

data.event: The deaths could be a result of a drier than normal winter, causing algal and bacterial blooms in the Esperance Lakes Nature Reserves.
Esperance recorded 457mm rainfall in 2006; the average is 620mm.
